N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 30.7 - Conformity with other laws

State Regulations

Nothing in this Part shall be construed in a manner inconsistent with, or in violation of, Insurance Law sections 2119, 2324, 4224, or other provisions of the Insurance Law and regulations promulgated thereunder. Notes
